	<p id="_5129438e-27ee-4576-bc4a-0297876212ca">D<sub>2</sub>O is a suitable choice as solvent for use with DSS-<stem type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mrow><mi>d</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow></msub></math></stem>.</p>
